the-amish-collection.Name: Galveston Dining Set
the-amish-collection.Body:
Each table is hand crafted from solid Quarter-sawn Oak. The table top features gear-drive leaf glides for easy & even opening & closing. Each table leaf is hand-crafted, numbered & matched, specifically for your table, resulting in a perfect table top fit. This double pedestal table features self-storing of 2 leaves. Resistovar finish is applied to the table top for worry free use.

The chair construction features both glued and pinned/screwed joints for strength and durability.
